Bine ai venit in MyBRD Mobile
Daca ai rabdare, in urmatoarele ecrane iti vom prezenta cateva din functionalitatile de care te vei bucura in utilizarea aplicatiei
Acces non stop la soldul contului tau
Plateste-ti facturile de utilitati, cu un simplu scan
Transferurile nu au fost niciodata mai usor de efectuat
Incasarile tale Western Union direct in contul tau
Daca ai un telefon cu o astfel de capabilitate, este foarte simplu sa te autentifici sau sa semnezi tranzactii in MyBRD Mobile", doar la o atingere distanta. "

O data autentificat, ai toate informatiile relevante legate de conturile, cardurile, economiile, investitiile", cat si toate operatiunile pe care le faci. Suplimentar primesti mesaje cu ultimele noastre oferte. "
Acum plata facturilor a devenit mult mai simpla. Scanezi codul de bare" direct de pe factura ta, sau daca nu o ai la indemana, selectezi detaliile furnizorului din sabloanele predefinite. "
Chit ca vorbim despre transferuri intre conturi, catre familie sau prieteni. Iar cu optiunea Trimite catre un cod QR, operatiunile catre utilizatorii MyBRD Mobile" se intampla instant. "
Cum ar fi sa primesti bani prin Western Union" si sa nu trebuiasca sa mergi in agentie pentru asta. Poti direct in aplicatie, doar cu detaliile tranzactiei. "
Este momentul sa descoperi singur toate functionalitatile MyBRD Mobile. Un lucru este sigur, viata cu siguranta iti va fi mai usoara cu aplicatia noastra de mobile banking". "

● The password must not contain forward or reverse numeric sequences of more than 2 digits. (e.g. accepted password 127854 and not 123785)
● The password must not contain more than 2 identical and consecutive digits (e.g. accepted password 225221 and not 622234)

"I agree that my digital fingerprint (hereinafter referred to as the Fingerprint) stored in this mobile device's memory will be used as a security element for (i) authentication in the MyBRD Mobile Application (hereinafter referred to as the Application) and for (ii) authorization of the following types of transactions: transfers between my accounts, foreign exchange transfers, transfers to pre-defined national beneficiaries, bill payments, QR code payments, receive money through Western Union, deposit creation and redemption, opening of current and savings accounts, made through the Application.
I understand that Fingerprint registration is not a condition for doing the above mentioned operations, and they can be done based on the PIN code. I have been informed that the Fingerprint option is enabled by PIN authorization.
If the Fingerprint authentication method is blocked (as a result of successive unsuccessful attempts to use the Fingerprint), the PIN may be used.
I have also been informed that I may revoke my consent to use the Fingerprint at any time by disabling it from the Settings menu of the Application.
I have acknowledged that the Bank reserves the right to disable the Fingerprint's use option if it detects security risks related to its scanning technology and will inform me of this measure before deactivation or, if it is not possible, immediately after disabling this option. I understand that I have the obligation to keep the mobile device secure against unauthorized access by third parties and not to record any third-party fingerprints for the purposes of the operations mentioned in (i) and (ii) above.
I know that the Fingerprint is a personal data that allows me to identify myself, which does not circumscribe the scope of my personal data processed by BRD for the purpose of providing the MyBRD Mobile service. I know that the mobile-specific technology that allows fingerprint scanning is not created by the Bank, so it is no"
